      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this character-filled and reliable ride! It's in fair condition, showing some honest signs of use and typical wear, but it remains a solid performer that's ready for its next chapter. This is a great opportunity to own a dependable vehicle with plenty of life left at a very accessible price!",
