    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior is free of any scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The interior shows no signs of use and is in like-new condition. All mechanical systems and electronics function perfectly.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't looking for perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and a few stains from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need some routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or a donor for parts. The engine requires a major overhaul and currently struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission shows signs of slipping. Externally, the body has significant rust along the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functioning air conditioning and power windows. It will require a trailer for transport and a substantial mechanical investment to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 5200.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sustained care. This unit has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust drivetrain, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for those who prioritize both value and quality. A premier choice for the discerning professional.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. It has a few tiny signs of character from the road, but overall it\u2019s a fantastic, comfy vehicle that won't let you down. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come swing by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerhouse delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed with a functional variable M differential lock providing excellent traction out of corners. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe inspection. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, the compression is within spec, and the suspension bushings remain compliant. A mechanically honest example of the E46 platform's peak engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Minor cosmetic wear. Reliable engine. Tires in good shape.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of engineering meeting everyday reliability. Having been meticulously maintained, it starts up smoothly every time and handles the road with a balanced, confident feel. The exterior still catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scratch near the trunk\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but never abused. Inside, the cabin remains a quiet sanctuary; the premium upholstery is clean and free of tears, though there is some light wear on the driver-side bolster. Every button and feature, from the heated seats to the intuitive infotainment system, works exactly as it should. It\u2019s a well-cared-for machine that offers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag. Recently serviced and fitted with tires that have plenty of life left, it's ready to go from day one.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, currently offered in commendable condition. This example exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and reliability, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. An ideal acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a premium experience at a competitive valuation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    }
  ],
